---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Integrating Traditional and Modern Elements in Nepali Homes";
const description = "Explore how Nepali house designs beautifully combine traditional architectural elements with modern conveniences to create unique and functional living spaces.";
const date = "2024-04-10";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="blog-post">
    <header>
      <p class="date">{new Date(date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
        year: 'numeric',
        month: 'long',
        day: 'numeric'
      })}</p>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
    </header>

    <img 
      src="https://nepalhomesearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/house-for-sale-budhanilakntha12-1.jpg"
      alt="Traditional and Modern Nepali House Design"
      class="hero-image"
    />

    <div class="content">
      <p class="lead">The fusion of traditional Nepali architecture with modern design elements creates homes that honor cultural heritage while meeting todayâ€™s lifestyle demands.</p>

      <h2>Blending Architectural Styles</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Traditional wooden carvings paired with sleek interiors</li>
        <li>Open courtyards (Chowks) integrated with modern open-plan layouts</li>
        <li>Exposed brickwork with contemporary finishes</li>
        <li>Use of traditional red and earth tones with modern colors</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Modern Amenities in Traditional Structures</h2>
      <p>Modern conveniences are seamlessly added to traditional frameworks:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Upgraded insulation for energy efficiency</li>
        <li>High-tech kitchens and bathrooms</li>
        <li>Smart home features for comfort</li>
        <li>Eco-friendly and sustainable materials</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Preserving Nepali Heritage</h2>
      <p>Preserving cultural elements is crucial in blending old and new:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Incorporating Aaley Jhyal (traditional windows) in modern structures</li>
        <li>Emphasis on natural materials</li>
        <li>Restoring old woodwork and carvings</li>
        <li>Using handcrafted elements to maintain authenticity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
<style>
  .blog-post {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .date {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .content {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }
  img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>